@startuml

title AircraftWar 简单工厂模式（道具创建）

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

class Game {
  - tryGenerateProp(enemyAircraft) : void
}

class PropSimpleFactory {
  + {static} createRandomProp(locationX : int, locationY : int, speedX : int, speedY : int) : AbstractProp
}

abstract class AbstractProp
class BloodSupply
class FireSupply
class FirePlusSupply

AbstractProp <|-- BloodSupply
AbstractProp <|-- FireSupply
AbstractProp <|-- FirePlusSupply

Game ..> PropSimpleFactory : 使用
PropSimpleFactory ..> AbstractProp : 创建

note right of PropSimpleFactory
  根据随机数创建具体道具实例：
  BloodSupply / FireSupply / FirePlusSupply
end note

@enduml
